Elder Jian struck his staff against stone. Sparks leapt into the air, silencing the crowd. His voice rumbled like distant thunder.
“Disciples of the Mountain\! Today you contend not only for honor, but for recognition. Skill will be tested. Will shall be weighed. Let all witness who endures, and who falters.”
